前20歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中學已經j過佢套女僕 聽佢啲叫聲有獸慾加成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed7eee8eb6c60110cc83a35dff8710bdf2f8e9bb","tid":584134,"uid":60785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T00:30:52.000Z","msg":"犀利"},{"pid":"0792781d04e9ed7dbb9a576d8189afb9e7d6fa0a","tid":584134,"uid":17776,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"1cf6b91db365a73706124db4378d7d34322cf392","tid":584134,"uid":109102,"like":94,"dislike":1,"score":93,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T16:23:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/08/002356_f806c4b2bca369c185ec39cbce77c754.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F08%2F002356_f806c4b2bca369c185ec39cbce77c754.png&h=67968da7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T00:31:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/08/083121_83cbbc5165616de8a8bf0d762dd4aa5b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F08%2F083121_83cbbc5165616de8a8bf0d762dd4aa5b.png&h=f6fac4c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6ac5d73ba645b03012e47ec9ffb7da4a2cc78db","tid":584134,"uid":92758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c277ce6bd729a36ef3d06e47c8b77969e5d3a2b7","tid":584134,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:00:46.000Z","msg":"日本AV男優德田重男今年已高齡82歲，是世界最老的現役男優，至今作品已累計超過350部，女主角的年齡從20到70歲都有，近日才剛結束一部A片的拍攝，女主角僅20歲，讓網友非常羨慕，「82歲了還可以跟20歲的女優拍片，死而無憾啦。」更有網友笑稱德田重男是名符其實的不老「騎」士。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n德田重男在踏入AV界以前，只是旅行社的員工，每天過著朝九晚五的上班族生活，60歲那年意外被發掘去拍A片，原本只是演無關緊要的角色，但由於形象太鮮明，最後變成男主角，甚至為此辭掉旅行社的工作，對此八田重男表示，「不知道可以活多久，但我要享受每一刻。只要身體還行，想做到85歲。」<br />\n<br />\n這位高齡男優其實家庭美滿，有妻有女，一開始瞞著家人拍AV，被家人拆穿後，女兒覺得成何體統，老婆則是認為，至少退休後不是閒在家裡沒事做，但很擔心身體撐不撐得住。目前德田重男累積超過350部作品，最讓網友羨慕的就是近期推出的「阿公最愛波霸惹系列」<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phprRDcTs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phprRDcTs.jpg&h=e4dcd406&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n，片中與20歲女優床上大戰，讓網友超級忌妒，「他是繼加藤鷹之後，最令人羨慕的男人。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpmuvAd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpmuvAd8.jpg&h=7a6aaac7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T00:39:34.000Z","msg":"SKD-030"},{"pid":"4c36e10f4cd1563f86324a10e12220f0cbcd9cf8","tid":584134,"uid":20130,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f5bab0fa6bd84edf6ee7425a22a0f45e2b2e9d64","tid":584134,"uid":57329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"817f469f61e02fd89a48335220d70c043823ece9","tid":584134,"uid":5190,"like":35,"dislike":7,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"c33b04d9021d63da6bc8bc764b2639f088959d95","tid":584134,"uid":1067,"like":194,"dislike":2,"score":192,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:02:42.000Z","msg":"20歲男優大戰82歲女優<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:05:27.000Z","msg":"大把"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:49:07.000Z","msg":"仲扯得起係幾勁嘅"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T01:07:29.000Z","msg":"阿婆一除左副假牙，20歲男優只剩下呻吟"},{"pid":"7c6368160b7726e0227697050f0ece405df6def8","tid":584134,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c36e10f4cd1563f86324a10e12220f0cbcd9cf8","tid":584134,"uid":20130,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f5bab0fa6bd84edf6ee7425a22a0f45e2b2e9d64","tid":584134,"uid":57329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"817f469f61e02fd89a48335220d70c043823ece9","tid":584134,"uid":5190,"like":35,"dislike":7,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:05:27.000Z","msg":"大把"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:49:07.000Z","msg":"仲扯得起係幾勁嘅"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T01:07:29.000Z","msg":"阿婆一除左副假牙，20歲